---
title: Cranberry Fig-Stuffed Chicken Thighs with Walnut-Dusted Broccoli
description: Sweet, sticky figgy goodness all wrapped up in juicy and tender chicken breasts, with a cloud of creamy mashed potato and nutty, buttery broccoli to go alongside. It's the classy weeknight dinner you've been waiting for!
